text: The security is not helpful and not friendly at all. He even throw my nric with a “plak” sound. Even when he sees that I have trouble getting pass the gate, he did not offer to help. After I asked for help a couple of times and I got fed up then he bothered to stand up and walk to me. Everything else is good including the people except for the security.
Person in govtech sg shirt brake tested me when i was walking in buona vista. I have an injured leg and it was painful to have to swerve around. We made eye contact and he didnt say anything.
